#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.compare.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.compare"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:1 of
msgid "Compare to another Series and show the differences."
msgstr "与另一个 Series 比较并显示差异。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:3 of
msgid "Object to compare with."
msgstr "用于比较的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:5 of
msgid ""
"Determine which axis to align the comparison on.  * 0, or 'index' : "
"Resulting differences are stacked vertically     with rows drawn "
"alternately from self and other. * 1, or 'columns' : Resulting "
"differences are aligned horizontally     with columns drawn alternately "
"from self and other."
msgstr ""
"确定比较结果对齐的轴。  * 0 或 'index'：结果差异垂直堆叠，行交替地从 self"
" 和 other 中提取。* 1 或 'columns'：结果差异水平对齐，列交替地从 self 和 "
"other 中提取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:5 of
msgid "Determine which axis to align the comparison on."
msgstr "确定在哪个轴上对齐比较。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:7 of
msgid "0, or 'index'"
msgstr "0，或 'index'"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:-1 of
msgid "Resulting differences are stacked vertically"
msgstr "结果差异垂直堆叠"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:8 of
msgid "with rows drawn alternately from self and other."
msgstr "行从自身和另一个对象交替提取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:9 of
msgid "1, or 'columns'"
msgstr "1，或 'columns'"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:-1 of
msgid "Resulting differences are aligned horizontally"
msgstr "结果差异水平对齐"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:10 of
msgid "with columns drawn alternately from self and other."
msgstr "列从自身和另一个对象交替提取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:12 of
msgid ""
"If true, all rows and columns are kept. Otherwise, only the ones with "
"different values are kept."
msgstr "如果为 True，则保留所有行和列。否则，只保留值不同的项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:15 of
msgid ""
"If true, the result keeps values that are equal. Otherwise, equal values "
"are shown as NaNs."
msgstr "如果为 True，则结果保留相等的值。否则，相等的值显示为 NaN。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:18 of
msgid "Set the dataframes names in the comparison."
msgstr "在比较中设置 DataFrame 的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:21 of
msgid ""
"If axis is 0 or 'index' the result will be a Series. The resulting index "
"will be a MultiIndex with 'self' and 'other' stacked alternately at the "
"inner level.  If axis is 1 or 'columns' the result will be a DataFrame. "
"It will have two columns namely 'self' and 'other'."
msgstr ""
"如果 axis 为 0 或 'index'，结果将是一个 Series。其索引将是一个 MultiIndex"
"，'self' 和 'other' 在内层交替堆叠。如果 axis 为 1 或 'columns'，结果将是"
"一个 DataFrame，它将包含两个列，即 'self' 和 'other'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:21 of
msgid ""
"If axis is 0 or 'index' the result will be a Series. The resulting index "
"will be a MultiIndex with 'self' and 'other' stacked alternately at the "
"inner level."
msgstr ""
"如果 axis 为 0 或 'index'，结果将是一个 Series。其索引将是一个 MultiIndex"
"，'self' 和 'other' 在内层交替堆叠。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:25 of
msgid ""
"If axis is 1 or 'columns' the result will be a DataFrame. It will have "
"two columns namely 'self' and 'other'."
msgstr ""
"如果 axis 是 1 或 'columns'，结果将是 DataFrame。它将有两列，分别是 'self"
"' 和 'other'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.compare`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:32 of
msgid "Compare with another DataFrame and show differences."
msgstr "与另一个 DataFrame 比较并显示差异。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:35 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:36 of
msgid "Matching NaNs will not appear as a difference."
msgstr "匹配的 NaN 不会被视为差异。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:39 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:44 of
msgid "Align the differences on columns"
msgstr "将差异按列对齐"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:51 of
msgid "Stack the differences on indices"
msgstr "将差异按索引堆叠"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:60 of
msgid "Keep all original rows"
msgstr "保留所有原始行"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.compare.series_compare:70 of
msgid "Keep all original rows and also all original values"
msgstr "保留所有原始行和所有原始值"

